author: Xbox
description:
Lab Rat is a hand-crafted narrative puzzler masquerading as a machine-generated video game. This satirical adventure stars a metrics-obsessed AI who will monitor, profile, and guide you as you solve over a hundred unique spatial problems. Over time this AI will develop a hilariously misguided understanding of humanity based on your performance and survey response data.

author: Xbox
description:
Lushfoil Photography Sim is a first person photography sim. Experience true-to-life recreations of beautiful and diverse locations around the world. Out now on Xbox Series X|S! 

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/lushfoil-photography-sim/9MXWLBJZHC39

Trek through and explore environments to capture stunning vistas and landscapes with your fully-featured in-game camera. Each environment is filled with objectives to reward players that have a good eye for angles and perspectives, and hidden secrets for those who are patient and observant.

Developed by Matt Newell. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2025
